description:
Ranked #11 among the Claymores.
While is just a regular girl, she uses her Yoki to give her the appearance of massive muscles. She appear brutish, short-tempered and violent to others.
She uses 2 swords, a rare permission to have, and she got her 2nd sword from her dead friend whom died in battle they had with the Yoma.
Captain of Team Undine in Pieta, first city of Alphonse (North).
name: Undine
